@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
<p>
    Welcome to Milkman Farms — where classic dairy-shop charm meets bold, handcrafted flavor.<br />
</p>
<p>
    At Milkman Farms, we believe dairy products should feel nostalgic, comforting, and a little adventurous. 
    From timeless vanilla bean favorites to creative blends like Banana Java Chip,
    every flavor is made to bring personality, warmth, and premium taste into every beverage and bite.<br />
</p>
<p>
    Inspired by vintage milk delivery culture and modern dessert craftsmanship, 
    Milkman Farms was built around one simple idea: bringing families the simple joy of the milkman.<br /> 
    Our brand blends old-school farm aesthetics with playful creativity to create products that feel both familiar and fresh.
</p>
<p>
    Whether you're grabbing a late-night pint, stocking the freezer for family movie night, or discovering your new favorite milk flavor, we’re here to make every time 'milk time'.
</p>
<p>
    Milkman Farms
    Fresh flavor. Classic charm. Delivered with personality.<br />
    - Martin Cow
</p>